0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:31:04.000Z","msg":"謝謝你們<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6470989c44dbd848118134649514d3b4b86ca1ed","tid":1868114,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:31:16.000Z","msg":"多謝醫護<br />\n<br />\n感激醫護<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e43156a804846703fc017c9edd44128d9ff4074","tid":1868114,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1fcc5ea927ea57b478b88e369bc5d7aff53128","tid":1868114,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:31:30.000Z","msg":"多謝醫護"},{"pid":"c78f556bb5827a70f65121ba780c8a4e21c11ede","tid":1868114,"uid":334299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:31:50.000Z","msg":"感激醫護"},{"pid":"84a236d9dea0f32b77c8ac7a48f7270e0576243d","tid":1868114,"uid":269226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"感激所有罷工嘅醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8905d6feca39f564202c4a461bab6280276f2c6","tid":1868114,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:32:36.000Z","msg":"用把口支持係無用，要用實際行動<br />\n<br />\n既然香港暫時勇武同罷工都係唔可行，咁唯有 焦土<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1868045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1868045</a><br />\n<br />\n[香港人，反抗] 要贏，必須升級至 全民三罷，甚至 全民勇武<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1866282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1866282</a><br />\n<br />\n無論係 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇武</span></strong></span> 或者 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">罷緊工</span></span></strong> 既手足 都捱唔到好耐<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「我地以為一二一二係衝，點知人地一二一二係退既。」<br />\n<br />\n「望返後面已經冇晒人。」<br />\n<br />\n「如果佢話三罷，或者罷鐵、罷藍舖頭，講完你要真係做先得架。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n擺在面前有兩套方法，<br />\n其一是  <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">全民有心理準備作正面衝突</span>，<br />\n其二是  <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">全民落實罷工</span><br />\n<br />\n「但係好多人就係覺得，去到呢個樽頸唔知點做。其實佢心入面明明就知呢兩樣野。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「希望大家唔好淨係識得講香港人反抗，反抗係做出?架，唔係你鳩?架！」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「我地個個都有夢想架，我地個個都有?野想做，但係，我地肯犧牲??野?上前線爭取啊！」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n勇武 同 醫護 都唔係condom，<br />\n所有珍惜生命既香港人，<br />\n以及願意付出更多既抗爭者，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">請你地加入呢次罷工！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n對於全民勇武已經唔抱太大既希望，但係呢次武漢肺炎係一個發動罷工既大好機會<br />\n希望全香港人可以真正團結一次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vzoa9L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vzoa9L.png&h=f8666165&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8413e95346d096293775742bf5e59e77a1887fff","tid":1868114,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:32:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abfe976995073ca3a0632b08835c319c23e90707","tid":1868114,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote"